          >
            <span class="text-base font-bold leading-7">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold leading-tight text-green-600">
              Create a Memorial Page
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base font-medium leading-7 text-dark-grey-600">
              Fill out a form with details of your loved one. Add a heartfelt
