            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rotate-90 lg:rotate-0">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="43"
            height="42"
            viewBox="0 0 43 42"
            fill="none"
          >
            <g clip-path="url(#clip0_3346_6663)">
